by Pannawat Muangmoon

Process
I started collecting unintentionally drawing lines on papers which someone trying pens ink testing in the stationery store, I am in love with the colors and the acquisition of drawing lines. I craft layer by layer, mixed with my favorite photo of organic stone structure, finish with computer programs.

The idea behind the project.
I focus the concept of 4 Earth's elements in the past have been experimenting with soil and water and had the opportunity to exhibit in the physical gallery. This stone collection is an extension art project from water elements made into NFT art. You can see my other works on my website.
